Package: untrader
Type: Package
Title: Wrapping the Comtrade API for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "Bochtler",email = 'paul.bochtler@swp-berlin.org', role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides a port to the Comtrade API, allowing the user to query trade data from the free endpoint for Goods. 
    This does not implement the endpoint for services or the premium or bulk-download facilities. 
